name: I Can Jump
description:
Simple platforming prototype I made a year ago, never released it because I never finished it! 
Thought I'd release it anyways lol :)
All you got to do is make it to the end.. which there is nothing special there lol. 

You can play this on your phone if you have a controller.  Enjoy!

AD or Right/Left Arrows to move, Space to Jump.
